    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Orbitron: Space Academy is a unique sci-fi PvP tactical arcade with two main modes — Pure tactical Space Chess mode or tactical mode combine with  real-time arcade battles, based on SteamNetwork.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Inspired by 1983's oldschool Archon, which I played with my father in the 90s. And many hours MOO2, which i played.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Real players only. No AI or single player for now!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Climb leaderboards with a custom ELO Ranking System.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Quick access to the game. Infinite gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/fdbd9188b2f339372d77dbbfa26f8adb.poster.avif?t=1764104363\" width=760 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/fdbd9188b2f339372d77dbbfa26f8adb.webm?t=1764104363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/fdbd9188b2f339372d77dbbfa26f8adb.mp4?t=1764104363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Please join our Discord and take part in playtesting!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Prove the quality and tactics of our new space chess and influence the rules.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Provide bugreports, feedback, ideas and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>No third party servers.</strong> Play until Steam is gone. <i>#stopkillinggames</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/ce1a705572a029a6780786975b95c234.avif?t=1764104363\" width=760 height=98 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Space Chess Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience heroic space chess-like turn-based tactics on a spaceboard, where <strong>the</strong> <strong>king is not hiding</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 different base <strong>formations</strong> and <strong>commanders</strong> to choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powers and use the abilities of your main ships, <strong>Guardian (King) &amp; Messenger (Queen).</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three ways to win. Seize all powerfields, infiltrate the enemy or defeat the main enemy ships.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/6f0940fe6657fee9b4c11c60e95fbaa9.poster.avif?t=1764104363\" width=760 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/6f0940fe6657fee9b4c11c60e95fbaa9.webm?t=1764104363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Orbitron Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like above, but the decision to take an enemy figure is resolved in an arcade spaceship battle.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage your opponent with your ship, but remember: <strong>The Attacker has a significant start advantage.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find new <strong>technology</strong> and <strong>upgrades</strong> on board and dominate in battle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Repair</strong> and <strong>upgrade</strong> your ships as they get more battle-hardened.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prioritize ship systems. Manage energy balance between shields, engines and weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive and get more <strong>experienced crew.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/646e65d813a5358330af7406bce9f1ed.avif?t=1764104363\" width=760 height=285 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Fleet at your command.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reimagined figures. Refreshing new ways to play, while still maintaining a resemblance to the original chess pieces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each class is unique, both on board and in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Major changes in figure philosophy:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >King is heroic. No more hiding, lead your fleet! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Queen is not overpowered. Shares power with King.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If one of them is lost, the remaining one's movement is nerfed into 'Classic' King in chess.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More moving maneuvers on the board.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/a92e35e2ca9e36777ad4042f9c1011ce.webp?t=1764104363\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/a92e35e2ca9e36777ad4042f9c1011ce.poster.avif?t=1764104363\" class=\"bb_img\" width=760 height=124 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061980/extras/4f4b1cd84990f677cf3437caca110b57.avif?t=1764104363\" width=760 height=98 /></span><strong>We respect privacy and customers.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We value customers, that's why we chose to remain solid in a world of bad practices. No data mining, reselling or even collecting. Your data stays where it should and that means on <i>your</i> device.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join growing community.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord and Steam community, take part in early testing, provide critical feedback, suggestions and bug reports and help us deliver the intended experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Thank you and enjoy playing!</i></p>",
